{"tid":1538562,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大訴求 咪撚改口","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T23:43:25.000Z","uid":80630,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"4d1e75e725d0bafe0c630d969431da664fec8849","tid":1538562,"uid":80630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:17:14.000Z","msg":"叫四大訴求嗰班做乜撚嘢<br />\n<br />\n「五大訴求 缺一不可」係咩意思<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我要五樣嘢，少一樣都唔得</span></strong><br />\n無啦啦做咩好似有嘢袋落袋就刪咗佢<br />\n<br />\n你嗌四大訴求<br />\n一嚟confuse<br />\n二嚟搞到我地咁多個月嘅理念缺咗個角<br />\n<br />\n唔該叫返<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「五大訴求 缺一不可」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</strong></span>"},{"pid":"2941f73bd984bc07f41754def2ae9c557a7a2d78","tid":1538562,"uid":290815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:18:21.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a573237262ec223e03e462db4da7d3f764f4f9","tid":1538562,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"13810a7fa97b929ed868c9401dc1ac84cba5104e","tid":1538562,"uid":79599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:21:20.000Z","msg":"never forget, never forgive"},{"pid":"335a7960ae373bdeb8c39f4dbce1148556abe40b","tid":1538562,"uid":241904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:21:22.000Z","msg":"佢而家撤回根本係想我地8/9少人出黎,咁9/9美國復會就未必過到香港人權關係法<br />\n撤回係3個月前既訴求<br />\n而家係五大訴求,缺一不可<br />\n如果唔係只會每幾年就有一過revolution"},{"pid":"6489dcab2d76a5a02823c8a2e0a10f559a8ab89e","tid":1538562,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LgdcLSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLgdcLSU.jpg&h=7d8fce73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1ktasvY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1ktasvY.jpg&h=e8e5ebbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WwTmzaZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWwTmzaZ.jpg&h=1a577aad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a889SFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa889SFe.jpg&h=3fb438bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機場壓力測試，其實係連「機場」都唔需要入的<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531743</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"161732d494fba5ced934cd804034fdae2fe48197","tid":1538562,"uid":116021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec20d5ed2e4d6328dfde9b89dd1c209f6a6c24e6","tid":1538562,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"有冇見過兇殺案由政府新聞處公佈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1535010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1535010</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n睇埋回覆先留言，因為分析我放咗喺回覆<br />\n<br />\n成個熱門勁多都係講林鄭撤回嘅風，<br />\n但而家佢撤唔撤回都好，831太子站有冇死人、有冇極嚴重傷勢受害人，呢d都係要查啊！唔好俾佢轉移焦點啊！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好認真，點解一路發生咁多件事，都冇話撤回，突然今日會講起？到底呢幾日發生咗咩事逼到佢要做野？係咪真係其實死咗人？就算冇死人，到底情況係幾嚴重？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">要求黨鐵交出831太子站完整CCTV記錄啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"d78e0ab858e73a7c4e21d17d79e0e37258af37f1","tid":1538562,"uid":164239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:38:38.000Z","msg":"「今天是一場小小的勝利...... 但我意識到我們不能這樣完結。 如果我們接受這政府提出的條款，我們已失去的朋友們是不會原諒我們的。」<br />\n<br />\n《凛冬烈火：烏克蘭自由之戰》<br />\n<br />\nToday was a small victory&hellip;. I realized that we couldn't leave it like that. Our friends that we've lost would not forgive us if we accepted those terms from the government.<br />\n<br />\n《Winter On Fire》"},{"pid":"29c89762aed323b4b780e02c02cd4b62df57d3d5","tid":1538562,"uid":80630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n實冇死"},{"pid":"db43acd362d5749a934935e187e8fdb2758c3b03","tid":1538562,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:39:52.000Z","msg":"［幫手推］隔離熱門po話撤回條例會令下次遊行失去一大班和理非喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538366\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538366</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c33ab1ece6051903f4e8766657aa6aa27b744ec1","tid":1538562,